2026-01-02  Robert Charusta  <rch-public@posteo.net>

	* go-template-helper-mode.el: Initial release.
	(go-template-helper-mode): New minor mode.
	(go-template-helper--font-lock-comments): New matcher for {{/* ... */}}.
	(go-template-helper--keywords): Add font-lock rules for delimiters,
	variables, keywords, and builtins.
	(go-template-helper--enable): Add keywords and refontify.
	(go-template-helper--disable): Remove keywords and refontify.
